#: ../../topics/releases/0.10.4.rst:8
# 2aa6b39734c843cc992447c2bd3445bd
msgid "Salt 0.10.4 is a monumental release for the Salt team, with two new module systems, many additions to allow granular access to Salt, improved platform support and much more."
